let MutationsType = {
  SET_CURRENT_DATE: "setCurrentDate",
  GET_CURRENT_TIME: "getCurrentTime",
  CREATE_CALENDAR_LIST: "createCalendarList",
  ADD_EVENT: "addEvent",
  DEL_EVENT: "delEvent",
  NEXT_MONTH: "nextMonth",
  PREV_MONTH: "prevMonth",
  SET_SELECT_INDEX: "setSelectIndex",
  SET_SELECE_MONTH: "setSelectMonth",
  SET_SELECT_YEAR: "setSelectYear",
  TOGGLE_SHOW_EVENT: "toggleShowEvent",
  INIT_EVENT_LIST: "initEventList",
};

export default MutationsType;
